STATE of North Carolina
v.
Dwight PARKER, Sr. No. 306P04-3. Supreme Court of North Carolina. May 3, 2007. Dwight Parker, Sr., Pro Se. Kathleen U. Baldwin, Assistant Attorney General, Clark Everett, District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 17th day of April 2007 in this matter for a writ of mandamus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Pitt County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in Conference this the 3rd day of May 2007."
